            <t:div type="edition">
              <t:note>The division into text parts follows <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb195">Paris, Bibliothèque nationale de France, BnF Éthiopien d'Abbadie 195</t:ref>.</t:note>
               <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Chronology">
                  <t:label>On the chronology of the Prophets</t:label>
                     <t:ab>አብያተ፡ ነቢያት፡ ናሁ፡ ጸሐፍነ፡ ለነቢያት፡
                        አብያቲሆሙ፡ <t:sic>ወአህገሪሆሙ፡</t:sic> ወኀበ፡ ተቀብረ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ነቢይ።
                     ኢዮብ፡ ተነበየ፡ ፵ዓመተ፡ ወእምድኅሬሁ፡ ሙሴ፡ ተነበየ፡ ፵ዓመት፡ ቅድመ፡
                     ምጽአተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ በሥጋ፡ ፲ወ<t:gap reason="lost" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>፬፻፹ወ፭፡ ዓመታት፡ ወእምድኅሬሁ፡ ኢያሱ፡ ዘናዊ፡
                        ተነበየ፡ ወ፳ወ፯ዓመተ። ወእምድኅሬሁ፡ ሳሙኤል፡ ተነበየ፡ ፵ዓመተ። ቅድመ፡ እምጽአተ፡ እግዚእነ፡ በሥጋ፡ ፲፻፵ወ፭ዓመታት፨ 
                  </t:ab>
               </t:div>
               <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" subtype="chapter" xml:id="Isaiah">
                 <t:note>The edition <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MP4U6VCR"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Knibb1985LivesProphets2"/><title level="a">The Ethiopic Version of the Lives of the Prophets, II: Isaiah, Jeremiah, Haggai, Zechariah, Malachi, Elijah, Elisha, Nathan, Ahijah, and Joel</title><title level="j">Bulletin of the School of Oriental and African Studies, University of London</title><author><forename>Michael A.</forename><surname>Knibb</surname></author><date>1985</date><biblScope unit="volume">48</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">1</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">16-41</biblScope><note type="url">http://www.jstor.org/stable/618769</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Knibb1985LivesProphets2</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Knibb1985LivesProphets2</note></t:bibl> starts with this part.</t:note>
                  <t:label>On the Prophet Isaiah</t:label>
                  <t:ab>ወካዕበ፡ ንነግር፡ አብያቲሆሙ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ኀበ፡ ነበሩ፡ ወኀበ፡ ተቀብሩ፡ በከመ፡ ጸሐፈ፡
                  ቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3828Epiphani">ኢጲፋንዮስ፡ ጳጳስ፡ ዘቂጵሮስ</t:persName>። ኢሳይያስ፡ ነቢይ፡ እምኢየሩሳሌም፡ ውእቱ፡ ወሞተ፡ በእደ፡
                ምናሴ፡</t:ab>
            </t:div>
